content:
Hmm?
Oh, a squirrel!{短暂停}
...Never mind, not enough meat.

I was just chatting with Big Gem and Little Gem.{短暂停}
...What's with that question mark on your face?
Don't tell me the gems where you're from don't talk to you?

Every time I stare at butterflies,
they zoom off faster.{短暂停}
It's not like I'm going to catch them.

In my view, all things unknown and novel are wonderful!
...
Though that's not why I'm staring at you.{微笑}

...Oh,
<color=#d3b037>{me}</color> is outside too, {短暂停}
What a coincidence.
